{"tid":2174904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋畢業前有乜目標？","createTime":"2020-08-26T07:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:00:56.000Z","uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e87118c04025a6fc1329e177c4f10355296e4d50","tid":2174904,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱上咗大學，我上一個sem core讀唔順，結果連累埋其他科冇心機讀，一直處於自暴自棄、渾渾噩噩嘅狀態。直至最近先的起心肝要面對自己嘅軟弱，呢個sem開始再唔拯救自己就再冇機會，所以依家都仲係處於補救嘅階段。<br />\n<br />\n問咗自己究竟畢業前有乜目標，答案係「不斷向前，要去到比自己所想像更加高嘅位置，令第日目標出現嘅時候可以成為襯得上佢嘅人」<br />\n<br />\n你哋呢？不論學業、財政、愛情、工作、夢想都得"},{"pid":"c9903fd03c8e6582cbce834d386350f41a792874","tid":2174904,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"畢業後都冇"},{"pid":"6cfdc26a9b0eb7c82085f824d27c00da927e6bdf","tid":2174904,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9903fd03c8e6582cbce834d386350f41a792874","tid":2174904,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"畢業後都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e4b90c7c4ce690828bebbcd9e61423cff6d1ff","tid":2174904,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9903fd03c8e6582cbce834d386350f41a792874","tid":2174904,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"畢業後都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7243dbcfbd07a4565bdbe0aacf2b377a8283fc2","tid":2174904,"uid":309398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d1f98fcb666b6f18fff861de7b781634458427","tid":2174904,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,